  "description": "Teemo's collection, mushrooms, items, and blowguns!",
  "body": "<p>Become the Swift Scout - Teemo in Minecraft!</p>\n\nTeemo is the most known Yordle champion from League of Legends.\nHe blows darts, plants shrooms, and traps his enemies!\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><em><a href=\"https://youtu.be/1ZFg7jE2oL4\">Mod Testing Video</a></em></strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em><strong>Blowguns:</strong></em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>\"That's gotta sting.\"</strong></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>each tier has better damage, fire rate, and effect duration</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Mould, does nothing</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ax50SIK.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Wood (Any planks)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xmG5J3Z.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Bamboo</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f5dcyeh.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Iron</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w4GaRHS.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Gold</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ATZ0Mdi.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Diamond</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9SHCJmv.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Obsidian</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NpsBfju.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Quartz</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Uv6wfK1.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Emerald</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lgDm98Z.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Netherite</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OGJtseM.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em><strong>Mushrooms</strong></em></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Normal Mushroom, stacks to 5.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>\"Refill with mushrooms at anvils.\"</strong></em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Right-click to toss.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Refill with mushrooms (brown/red)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BPC4exB.png\" /></strong></em></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Magic Mushroom</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">, stacks to 5.</span><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>\"Refills automatically.\"</em></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Right-click to toss.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Refill automatically every 10s</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XJWmXH3.png\" /></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><em>Equipments</em></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>These magic items came with great power, in exchange, no armour value were provided.</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Deathcap&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>\"Devil Teemo Standard\"</strong></em></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">+6.0 Attack Damage</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/U21Argu.png\" /></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Scout Hat <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><em>\"Teemo Special: Gains invisibility while sneaking in the busehs\"</em></strong></span></p>\n<p>+10% Movement Speed</p>\n<p>+ Sneak in bushes will gain you invisibility</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlRbTqd.png\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Boots of Mobility&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em><strong>\"Most popular choice among all Teemo players.\"</strong></em></span></p>\n<p>+40% Movement Speed</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/10sGpq0.png\" /></p>",
